messages.message: Hello~ In the top nav bar, is the user icon supposed to be initials? Right now it seems to instead be the first two letters of my name (I checked with another person, they’re seeing the same). I’d expect it to be RB (initials) not RO (first two letters).
We currently don’t have the full name of a user available on front end so those initials are chopping off the first two values of the account email.
seems that a user profile has no name entry at all.
